quote_items.public_notes:
*Quoted lead time to initial samples after design approval: 12  Weeks
*Tool to be manufactured based on data received 5/19/2021 (00011357.STEP). Prints received  will be utilized for reference, and inspection criteria only.
*Tool price includes a setup and 10 initial samples. (Note: additional component quantities will be 
subject to lead times based on current capacity. Please contact your PM for specific timing.)
*Quoted: Single Cavity, Class 101, ( 18" x 20") Stainless Steel Standalone Tool, with hardened 
stainless steel, inserted core and cavity blocks, two slides required and Hot Half two drop direct gating also "A" side Ejection assist.63 core pin/sleeve ejectors on "B" side.
*Includes: Parting lines locks, cycle counter, insulator boards, box covers, guided ejection and 2D detail prints..

quote_items.public_notes:
*PRE-VALIDATION:
The following validation protocols and deliverables will be achieved by leveraging and utilizing the 
output of the 1st part in the family of parts:
• Validation Master Plan (VMP) Molded 
• Process Flow Plan, PFMEA, Process Control Plan 
* Scientific Injection Molding
 Pressure Setting Study: 7 settings 5 pieces each setting
 Check all CTQ's on 3 parts from each setting (21)
• Manufacturing Materials List. Molding, Tooling, Assembly, MSDS / SDS
• Material C of C Molding, SS Purchased screw & SS retaining ring, passivation (coating or rust 
prevention)
• Molding Protocols – IQ / OQ / PQ (the following protocols will be performed on the 1st part of the 
family of parts. All subsequent parts will receive modified (leveraged) IQ-OQ-PQ protocols
